high_descs: Turn and go to the grey table against the wall opposite the bed.
Pick up the pen that is sitting to the right of the laptop.
Turn around and go to the nightstand on the left of the bed.
Place the pen inside the mug on the nightstand.
Pick up the mug with the pen inside.
Turn around and go back to the table
Place the mug with the pen inside on the table in front of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Place a pen in a mug on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the gray table opposite the bed.
Pick up the pen from the table that is near the lap top.
Go to the night stand to the left of the bed.
Put the pen in the mug next to the phone on the night stand.
Take the mug from the night stand.
Turn right, go to the gray table opposite the bed.
Put the mug next to the right lower corner of the lap top on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on a table.

high_descs: Walk an an half circle to the right.
At the front of the counter with the computer on it. grab the ink pen from it.
Travel to the right with the marker in hand, travel right further.
Lower  your marker in the cup on the dresser.
Pick up the cup and the pen together in hand.
Turn  left and turn left again and turn to the right with the cup in hand.
Plant the cup on down by the table with the Television on it.
anns.task_desc: To sort a pen with a cup out together as for regular Television maintenance leave them on the table.
